text: Charlotte Ritchie (born 29 August 1989) is an English actress. She is best known for her roles as Alison Cooper in Ghosts, Oregon in the Channel 4 comedy Fresh Meat, Hannah in Siblings, Alison in Dead Pixels, Barbara Gilbert in the BBC drama Call the Midwife, George in Feel Good, Kate Galvin in You and Bonnie Davenport in Grantchester. She was a member of the classical crossover group All Angels.\- == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:English actors
